  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\n`quarkusDev#workingDir` has been deprecated\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/eb566083adc6b70b85af3669439b0641e7bcecc4/devtools/gradle/gradle-application-plugin/src/main/java/io/quarkus/gradle/tasks/QuarkusDev.java#L191-L195\r\n\r\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n```kotlin\r\ntasks.quarkusDev {\r\n  workingDirectory = rootProject.layout.projectDirectory.asFile\r\n}\r\n```\n\n### Actual behavior\n\n```kotlin\r\ntasks.quarkusDev {\r\n    workingDir = rootProject.projectDir.toString()\r\n}\r\n```\n\n### How to Reproduce?\n\nhttps://quarkus.io/guides/gradle-tooling#dev-mode\n\n### Output of `uname -a` or `ver`\n\n_No response_\n\n### Output of `java -version`\n\n_No response_\n\n### Quarkus version or git rev\n\n_No response_\n\n### Build tool (ie. output of `mvnw --version` or `gradlew --version`)\n\n_No response_\n\n### Additional information\n\nRelated: [Add 'rootProjectDirectory' to 'project.layout' (ProjectLayout)](https://github.com/gradle/gradle/issues/13654)",
